dt-option.default:
        The default value for the `-init searchPanes.dataLength` option is `-type undefined` as the standard should be without any custom classes.


		This is useful as it allows specific panes to be targetted for custom styling.





    $('#example').DataTable( {
        searchPanes:true,
        dom: 'Sfrtip',
        columnDefs:[
            {
                searchPanes: {
                    className: 'myCustomClass',
                },
                targets: [3]
            }
        ]
    });
